xserver-xorg-video-i810-modesetting (1.6.5.git20061014-1~1) experimental; urgency=low

  * Initial packaging of modesetting branch of xf86-video-intel (i810).
    This is a development snapshot only at the moment but should
    eventually replace the i810 driver in the future.
  * Patch 10_i830_modes_M_T_defines.patch enables build for this
    version (workaround reported on xorg mailing list).
  * configure script and friends generated with "autoreconf --install".
  * Upload to experimental using "~1" underversion.

 -- Drew Parsons <dparsons@debian.org>  Sun, 15 Oct 2006 01:31:33 +1000
